headline: Homes.Com Report: Home Price Increases Slowed in May for the Fifth Consecutive Month. Nationally, the Median Home Price Was Up Just 1.0% From a Year Ago.
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., June 18, 2025--Homes.com, a CoStar Group leading online residential marketplace, today released a new report analyzing home prices in May (based on the data collected to date), price trends across major metros, and what the latest developments in the housing market mean for homebuyers.
